# Vue Component Standards

## Template Structure
- Use `<template>` then `<script setup lang="ts">` order
- No `<style>` blocks — use Tailwind utility classes exclusively
- Use semantic HTML elements where appropriate

## Script Setup
- Always use `<script setup lang="ts">`
- Import types with `import type { X } from "~/lib/types"`
- Use `definePageMeta({ middleware: "auth" })` on all authenticated pages
- Composables are auto-imported — no need to import `useAuth`, `useStore`, etc.

## Tailwind CSS
- Use Tailwind v4 classes (no config file needed)
- Custom colors defined in `@theme`: `primary-50` through `primary-950`, `success-500`, `warning-500`, `danger-500`
- Responsive: mobile-first with `sm:`, `md:`, `lg:` breakpoints
- Common patterns:
  - Cards: `rounded-xl bg-white p-5 shadow-sm`
  - Inputs: `rounded-lg border border-gray-300 px-3 py-2.5 text-sm focus:border-primary-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500/20`
  - Primary buttons: `rounded-lg bg-primary-600 px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-white hover:bg-primary-700`
  - Status badges: `rounded-full px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium`

## Modals
- Use `<Teleport to="body">` for modals
- Backdrop: `fixed inset-0 z-50 flex items-center justify-center bg-black/50 p-4`
- Close on backdrop click: `@click.self="showModal = false"`

## Data Loading
- Fetch data in `onMounted()` hook
- Show loading spinner while fetching
- Handle empty states gracefully
